@startuml evolution_lineage
skinparam monochrome true
left to right direction

title Tracciamento discendenza e schema CBOR

package "Cloud/Hub - Linux Server" <<Linux Server>> {
  class "AgentLineageRecord" as AgentLineageRecord <<CBOR Schema>> {
    + UUID: bytes[16]
    + Parent_UUID: bytes[16] | null
    + Generation_Index: uint32
    + Archetype_Flag: bool
    + Birth_Timestamp: uint64
    + Mutation_Source: text
  }

  class "Rust Persistence Node" as RustPersistence <<Persistence>> {
    + persist_cbor(record: AgentLineageRecord)
    + publish_lineage_event(record)
    + rebuild_dag(): LineageDAG
    + query_by_generation(index: uint32)
  }
}

package "Observatory - Browser / Mobile" <<Browser/Mobile>> {
  class "LineageDAG" as LineageDAG <<Replay View>> {
    + add_vertex(UUID)
    + add_edge(Parent_UUID, UUID)
    + mark_archetype(UUID)
    + ancestors(UUID): Vec<UUID>
    + descendants(UUID): Vec<UUID>
  }
}

AgentLineageRecord "0..*" -- "0..1" AgentLineageRecord : descends from
RustPersistence --> AgentLineageRecord : stores immutable record
RustPersistence --> LineageDAG : publishes replay projection
LineageDAG --> AgentLineageRecord : indexes

note bottom of AgentLineageRecord
  **Hosted on:** Cloud/Hub - Linux Server
  **CBOR positional map:**
  0: UUID bytes[16]
  1: Parent_UUID bytes[16] | null
  2: Generation_Index uint32
  3: Archetype_Flag bool
  4: Birth_Timestamp uint64
  5: Mutation_Source text
end note

note right of RustPersistence
  Persistence contract:
  - decode CBOR payloads from lineage/evolution topics
  - store records append-only for auditability
  - rebuild ancestry as a DAG, not as a tree
  - preserve archetype milestones for observatory replay
end note

footer Hosting: Cloud/Hub Linux Server -> Rust Persistence and CBOR schema; Observatory Browser/Mobile -> LineageDAG replay view | MQTT Topics: tr4d3rz/lineage/lineage/{agent_id}, tr4d3rz/lineage/archetype/{archetype_id}, tr4d3rz/evolution/birth/{agent_id}, tr4d3rz/evolution/mutation/{node_id} | CBOR Payload: UUID, Parent_UUID, Generation_Index, Archetype_Flag, Birth_Timestamp, Mutation_Source
@enduml
